column1: # Title: Solar PV Resource Potential by ReEDS Region; PV Class; and Bin
# Comments: PV resource potential in MW for each region-class-bin. Bins are the portions of the interconnection supply curves. Summing across bins will provide total resource in a region and class.
# Source: Information based on ReEDS version 2017.  Files provided by ReEDS team in April 2017.
